{"tid":1558622,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"和勇不分，大家喺 9.11 抖一抖","createTime":"2019-09-10T13:55:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T15:12:52.000Z","uid":117731,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"92223bfc940eed00630b070560e8da84f0e3c642","tid":1558622,"uid":117731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:55:01.000Z","msg":"聽日911，無乜事就早d返屋企訓覺，有理由相信將會發生大事，中國人可能派人恐襲擊香港然後賴落示威者身上，令到美國不支持香港。<br />\n<br />\n因為其實我有合理理由 <br />\n懷疑聽日第一度會出事既 係元朗 同埋西灣河<br />\n兩個地方都係深藍地區<br />\n西灣河狗屋 頭先突然拆曬全部水馬 連停車場入面D水馬都拆埋<br />\n你地要知藍色線 北角打後個D地方都屬於深藍地區<br />\n頭先傍晚時分 西灣河狗屋個度拆曬<br />\n<br />\n無情白事會拆曬水馬圍欄？？唔怕比人圍狗屋？<br />\n加上肯定聽日會有人搞事<br />\n<br />\n你唔排除聽日會話有人闖入狗屋<br />\n跟住唔知襲警又呢樣個樣 咁樣嫁禍比我地自己友<br />\n唔排除聽日會有狗死 <br />\n你地要知呢個垃圾政府為左老屈人 可以去到幾盡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ntSbNh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ntSbNh.jpg&h=69ec3a3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AuVM0FC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAuVM0FC.jpg&h=8220fb77&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NjxWDsi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNjxWDsi.jpg&h=09287626&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/360tuyZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F360tuyZ.jpg&h=f7c1246c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然我都會尊重各位手足嘅最後決定！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">驅逐共黨<br />\n光復香港</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"4fa2ce1d8479f038e6e101c7b33ac1027419266f","tid":1558622,"uid":117731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:59:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"